  }
  *{{DI=.125;DI2=.7; MAXC=.31} s .8}
  2*{z -.15 s .97 lr 2 {DI=DI*2;DI2=DI2-DI2;MAXC=MAXC-.02} }
  *{{N=5000}}(N)*{{i=i+1;ang=rndf()*2*PI;r=rndf()*1.1}}
